.DT
static_query_short
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
static_query_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
static_query_short -  This method returns the short description of the room only from within the map handlers files.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string static_query_short(string room)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^room%^RESET%^ - the room to return the short description of
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the short description of the room only from
within the map handlers files.  This will not cause the room
to load and will not work on cloned file names.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_short()

.EP

